mc.parent("headBase", "head_ctrl")
mc.parentConstraint("head_ctrl", "head_lattice_hook_in", mo=1)


# HEAD SQUASH NORMALIZE
[mc.connectAttr("head_ctrl.s{}".format(axe), "tweaks_hook_in.s{}".format(axe), f=1) for axe in "xyz"]
[mc.connectAttr("head_ctrl.s{}".format(axe), "tweaks_squash_hook_in.s{}".format(axe), f=1) for axe in "xyz"]

mc.scaleConstraint('head_ctrl', 'head_lattice_hook_in', mo=1)

# normalize head's squash

md = mc.createNode("multiplyDivide", n="head_lattice_normalize_md")
mc.connectAttr("head_lattice_hook_in.sx", md+".input2X", f=1)
mc.connectAttr("head_ctrl.sx", md+".input1X", f=1)
mc.setAttr(md+".operation", 2)


pma = mc.createNode('plusMinusAverage', n='head_squash_normalize_pma')

value = mc.getAttr('head_arc_divided_Scale_md.input1X')

mc.setAttr(pma+'.input1D[0]', value)
mc.connectAttr(md+'.outputX', pma+'.input1D[1]', f=1)
mc.setAttr(pma+'.input1D[2]', -1)

mc.connectAttr(md+'.outputX', 'head_arc_divided_Scale_md.input2X', f=1)

mc.connectAttr(pma+'.output1D', 'head_spine_arclen_md.input2X', f=1)


global_md = mc.createNode("multiplyDivide", n="head_global_lattice_md")
mc.connectAttr("Krog_facial_master_ctrl.globalScale", global_md+".input1X")
mc.setAttr(global_md+".operation", 2)
mc.connectAttr(global_md + ".outputX", "head_arc_divided_Scale_md.input2X", f=1)


mc.connectAttr("head_ctrl.scaleX", "head_global_lattice_md.input2X", f=1)
mc.setAttr("head_global_lattice_md.operation", 1)

# pma tweaks scales
tweaks_pma = mc.createNode('plusMinusAverage', n='head_tweaks_scale_pma')
mc.connectAttr('Krog_facial_master_ctrl.globalScale', tweaks_pma+'.input1D[0]', f=1)
mc.connectAttr('head_ctrl.sx', tweaks_pma+'.input1D[1]', f=1)
mc.setAttr(tweaks_pma+'.input1D[2]', -1)
[mc.connectAttr(tweaks_pma+".output1D", "tweaks_hook_in.s{}".format(axe), f=1) for axe in "xyz"] 
[mc.connectAttr(tweaks_pma+".output1D", "tweaks_squash_hook_in.s{}".format(axe), f=1) for axe in "xyz"] 
[mc.connectAttr(tweaks_pma+".output1D", "R_up_squint_rb_scale_loc.s{}".format(axe), f=1) for axe in "xyz"] 
[mc.connectAttr(tweaks_pma+".output1D", "L_up_squint_rb_scale_loc.s{}".format(axe), f=1) for axe in "xyz"]
[mc.connectAttr(tweaks_pma+".output1D", "R_down_squint_rb_scale_loc.s{}".format(axe), f=1) for axe in "xyz"]
[mc.connectAttr(tweaks_pma+".output1D", "L_down_squint_rb_scale_loc.s{}".format(axe), f=1) for axe in "xyz"]



mc.parentConstraint("L_eyelids_squash_ct_not_used", "L_eyebrow_hook_in", mo=1)
mc.parentConstraint("R_eyelids_squash_ct_not_used", "R_eyebrow_hook_in", mo=1)
